! Definition

In Book VIII, Plato describes the "Drones" as the idle, consumerist class that emerges in democracies.

* **Stingless Drones:** The impoverished idlers who live on public charity or theft.
* **Stinging (Armed) Drones:** The ambitious demagogues who lead the masses, attack the wealthy, and eventually produce the Tyrant.

They represent the "unnecessary appetites" within the political body.